name: Cottontail
description: It's rabbit season! Fine folk up and down the bunny trail are dressed in their bun-day best, eggs painted and smiles wide. Here's hoping their hopping helps you with holiday cheer!

wikiSkinData.lore: Eggs are lame, right? They're round. They break easily. Eggs need a major facelift. Introducing… Teemo! He's cute. He's annoying. But most of all, he'll paint all your eggs for you, maybe turning one or two (or seven) into life-threatening explosives.
Rising from the fluffiest depths to crush all root vegetable cohorts, Fizz commands the greatest threat carrots have ever known—a killer rabbit with the foulest and cruelest of tempers.
